This paper deals with the problem of domain adaptation and generalization in medical imaging using deep learning models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with the problem of generalization, which is a common topic in the field of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with medical imaging, which falls under the category of Multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper uses deep learning models, which is a common topic in Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
